data.description: Discover the hidden gem at 3236 Yorktown Dr, Tallahassee, FL 32312, where potential meets affordability in a home that's ripe for personalization. This property is an ideal canvas for those looking to invest a bit of TLC and creativity to cultivate substantial sweat equity. This promising residence is equipped with a series of significant upgrades, laying a robust foundation for transformation. A brand new roof provides long-term peace of mind, while newly installed windows fill the home with natural light, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The addition of a new sliding glass door enhances the flow to outdoor living spaces, and new flooring in all bedrooms except the master bedroom adds to the home's appeal. A highlight of this opportunity is the inclusion of all new kitchen cabinets and a new stove, setting the stage for a modern and functional kitchen space that awaits your culinary adventures. Priced for a quick sale, 3236 Yorktown Dr stands as an excellent opportunity for first-time buyers dreaming of customizing their first home or investors seeking a profitable project in a desirable neighborhood. Don't let this chance slip by. Schedule your showing today and start imagining the endless possibilities that await at 3236 Yorktown Dr.
